---
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="chip">// the.problem</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Raw power without a harness.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Models get faster every month. The bottleneck was never the engine — it was the lack of a harness.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pane">
    <div class="pane-header">
      <div class="pane-dots">
        <span class="pane-dot"></span>
        <span class="pane-dot"></span>
        <span class="pane-dot"></span>
      </div>
      <span class="pane-path">~/agents/before-after.diff</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pane-body">
      <div class="diff-grid">
        <!-- BEFORE -->
        <div class="diff-col">
          <div class="diff-head diff-head--before">
            <span class="diff-marker">-</span> without orchestration
          </div>
          <ul class="diff-list">
            <li><span class="diff-num">01</span><span class="diff-title">One prompt at a time</span><span class="diff-desc">You prompt, agent implements, you review. For every task. Every file.</span></li>
            <li><span class="diff-num">02</span><span class="diff-title">No dependency awareness</span><span class="diff-desc">Agents work in isolation. No knowledge of what others did or need.</span></li>
            <li><span class="diff-num">03</span><span class="diff-title">Manual breakdown</span><span class="diff-desc">You're the planner, the PM, and the reviewer. Agent does the last mile only.</span></li>
            <li><span class="diff-num">04</span><span class="diff-title">Context starts from zero</span><span class="diff-desc">Every session loses requirements. You re-explain every time.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- AFTER -->
        <div class="diff-col">
          <div class="diff-head diff-head--after">
            <span class="diff-marker">+</span> with molt code
          </div>
          <ul class="diff-list">
            <li><span class="diff-num diff-num--accent">01</span><span class="diff-title">Spec once, build everything</span><span class="diff-desc">Write one PRD. The pipeline creates issues, assigns agents, ships features.</span></li>
            <li><span class="diff-num diff-num--accent">02</span><span class="diff-title">Dependency-aware execution</span><span class="diff-desc">Issues tracked with blockers. Agents build in the right sequence.</span></li>
            <li><span class="diff-num diff-num--accent">03</span><span class="diff-title">Agents plan and execute</span><span class="diff-desc">Planner researches your code and writes the plan. Resolvers implement.</span></li>
            <li><span class="diff-num diff-num--accent">04</span><span class="diff-title">Persistent context</span><span class="diff-desc">PRDs, issues, docs travel with every session. Agents always know the goal.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-head {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .diff-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .diff-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .diff-col + .diff-col {
      padding-left: 2rem;
      border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .diff-col:first-child {
      padding-right: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .diff-head {
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .diff-marker {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-right: 0.375rem;
  }

  .diff-head--before .diff-marker { color: #C75C5C; }
  .diff-head--after .diff-marker { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .diff-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .diff-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.25rem 0.875rem;
  }

  .diff-num {
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    grid-row: span 2;
    padding-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  .diff-num--accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .diff-title {
    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .diff-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
